<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Sardinia Terrace</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">24<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi>Feb<hi rend="sup">y</hi></p>
<lb/><p>1858 </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>Mary Ann</persName></p>
<lb/><p>A text which 
<lb/>has been present 
<lb/>to my mind in 
<lb/>every difficulty 
<lb/>in which I have 
<lb/>been placed may 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002657_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>be commended 
<lb/>to your attention 
<lb/>as of great value 
<lb/>to you who are 
<lb/>but beginning 
<lb/>the path of life<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>It is this, "commit 
<lb/>thy way unto the 
<lb/>Lord, trust also 
<lb/>in him and he 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002657_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'-->
<lb/>shall bring it to 
<lb/>pass"<reg>.</reg> Do this 
<lb/>and you will 
<lb/>be guided safely 
<lb/>and may he 
<lb/>lead you to his 
<lb/>Heavenly kingdom </p>
<lb/><p>I am &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><p><persName>Miss Young</persName></p>
			
